  <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:1;4:10">Searching and Browsing</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:14">CWRC utilizes a robust search system to make the contents of the site as accessible and
    explorable as possible. </shortdesc>
  <refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="refbody:1;7:12">
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="section:1;8:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:2;9:14">Search (general)</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:1;10:10">The search bar is located at the top of all pages of the CWRC site. You can narrow down
        where in CWRC you are searching from the search bar by selecting either <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:1;11:84">Collaboratory</b>
        (the default option) or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:2;12:36">Website Content</b>. If you would like more search options, there
        is an <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:3;13:18">Advanced Search</b> link to the right of the search box. <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Affc2c9b1-d242-4077-8a13-36c3b7d07127/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_ulx_h3z_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:1;15:49"/></p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="section:2;17:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:3;18:14">Search Results</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:2;19:10"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:4;19:13">Search Results</b> can be sorted by the relevance to search terms, title, creation date,
        and last modified date. These option can be organized in ascending and descending order.
          <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A30a30098-4750-4676-8f7e-89fb9332c4e4/datastream/OBJ/view" scale="80" align="center" id="image_og3_4fz_fy" scalefit="yes" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:2;23:75"/></p>
      <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Acf7280be-eb73-4d00-b7e0-6b3a7090878e/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_usp_q3z_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:3;26:47"/>
      <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A45bb334b-e087-4fc0-a8cd-7fc85c15c633/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_e54_y3z_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:4;29:47"/>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:3;30:10">Additionally you can view your search results in a list (default) or grid view. <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A70eeda06-c87f-4d80-8b2e-91be6ed66bb5/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_kpq_bjz_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:5;33:49"/></p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:4;34:10">Users can also view search results by <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:5;34:51">Bibliographic View</b>, which displays search
        results as citations. These can be organized by type of citation style (see screenshot
          below).<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Ad975acd5-b70b-4671-b2cd-b454ccce5622/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_r5z_gjz_3x" align="center" scale="80" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:6;38:60"/></p>
      <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A5739e251-d90c-478f-908c-a91d3aea796f/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_vtj_jjz_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:7;41:47"/>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:5;42:10">Another available view of search results in by <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:6;42:60">Documents</b>. This lets users view the
        search results as “abstracts.” the information presented includes the latest workflow stamp,
        title, author, description, etc. However, this view depends on the metadata and not all
        files have all those fields filled in.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A905bad40-3bbf-46a3-9117-2fed410426e2/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_nbh_4jz_3x" align="center" scale="80" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:8;47:60"/></p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="section:3;49:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:4;50:14">Advanced Search</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:6;51:10">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:7;51:17">Advanced search</b> option allows users to enter multiple search terms (separated by
        boolean operators - and, or and not). You can have from one to multiple search terms. The
        red “+” and “-” buttons beside the search terms will add or delete them. You can specify
        where the search term should be found by changing the “Field” option.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Ae32d77f7-dbea-4ebd-bb55-72b6f98b2ac5/datastream/OBJ/view" scale="80" align="center" id="image_j1t_pfz_fy" scalefit="yes" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:9;57:75"/></p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:7;58:10">The “field” list narrows down your search by the metadata and workflow stamps of objects.
        The default option is dc.title, which will return the most results because when an object is
        created or uploaded it is a required field. <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A80dad9a5-773a-4c54-be59-caaf5322ae3c/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_eq1_skz_3x" align="center" scale="80" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:10;62:60"/></p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="section:4;64:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:5;65:14">Save Search</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:8;66:10">When you conduct a search, using the search bar or the advanced search option, you can save
        your search. This is particularly useful if you have many search results to go explore.
          <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Abeb6b9f6-2afa-4b39-b261-c1d164a4f835/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_evl_vkz_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:11;70:49"/></p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:9;71:10">You access your saved searches in your account dashboard. Clicking on the saved search
        title will take you back to the search results.<image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A3d326292-3d6f-4738-9de6-11a658b11896/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_pp2_1lz_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:12;74:49"/></p>
    </section>
    <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="section:5;76:14">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="title:6;77:14">Browsing</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:10;78:10">There are multiple ways to browse the content of CWRC writer. You can travel through the
        Collaboratory projects sorting them by title or by recent modifications. <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Ae5f65d5c-339f-46c5-9cf4-0a49c1732dbc/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_gtp_dlz_3x" align="center" scale="80" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:13;82:60"/></p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="p:11;83:10">Additionally, CWRC provides a faceted browsing feature. This is when you narrow down items
        (in this case search results) by different filter. Narrow down search results by as many
        filters as you would like. To add or remove filters you can click on the “+” or “-” buttons
        beside each individual feature. The filters include:<ul id="ul_vlf_rgz_3x" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="ul:1;86:84">
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:1;87:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:8;87:18">Language:</b> choose to view only english or french files.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:2;88:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:9;88:18">Source:</b> view results by the project they are from.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:3;89:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:10;89:18">Type:</b> is the content model that the document was uploaded using.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:4;90:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:11;90:18">Authority:</b> this refers to if it is published or under review.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:5;91:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:12;91:18">Format:</b> this refers to the medium of an item (book, audio, etc.)</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:6;92:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:13;92:18">Genre:</b> refers to the classification of the item (nonfiction, etc.)</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:7;93:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:14;93:18">Folksonomic genre:</b> user generated genre classification.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:8;94:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:15;94:18">Publication date:</b> when it was published.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="li:9;95:15"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="b:16;95:18">Century:</b> what century the item was created. <image placement="break" href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Acfda5524-c424-402f-ba9c-ec619be16e4c/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_evw_llz_3x" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="image:14;97:53"/></li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
  </refbody>
  <related-links class="- topic/related-links " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="related-links:1;101:18">
    <link href="Searching_CWRC.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="link:1;102:39" type="task"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Searching CWRC</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC provides users with a search and advanced search functions. Searchable items         include projects, collection, files and topics of interest. </desc></link>
    <link href="About_CWRC.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="link:2;103:35" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">About CWRC</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC is an online research environment that brings together scholarly materials and digital tools. </desc></link>
    <link href="CWRC_Content_Models.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="link:3;104:44" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">CWRC Content Models</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The organization, creation, and upload of materials relies on content models. These     define the parameters of a subcollection, determining is you can add a subcollection and what     type of material can be added.</desc></link>
    <link href="User_Roles.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="link:4;105:35" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">CWRC user roles</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC users have different levels of access to their projects. This ranges from     non-members who can only view the materials on CWRC to project administrators who has complete     control over project materials.</desc></link>
    <link href="User_Account.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-CWRC/Searching_Browsing_CWRC.dita" xtrc="link:5;106:37" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">User Account</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">CWRC provides an enriched user experience no matter what type of user account you have.     Features include an insite messaging system between project members and a bookmarking tool to     collection your favorite materials together.</desc></link>
